OL,3,CMotorist wins five-year legal battle
OL,4,Cwith parking firm over a #1 ticket
OL,6,FA man from Leicestershire has won a
OL,7,Ffive-year legal battle with a major
OL,8,Fparking firm over a #1 ticket that he
OL,9,Fhad already paid for.
OL,11,FNigel Richardson, 71, took on Euro Car
OL,12,FParks after he was pursued over the
OL,13,Falleged #1 debt - even after supplying
OL,14,Fthe firm with the receipt proving he
OL,15,Fhad paid the correct fare at the time.
OL,17,FDuring the next four years, debt
OL,18,Fcollection companies sent him letters
OL,19,Fthreatening court action and the fine
OL,20,Fincreased to #230.
