OL,6,FMr Richardson refused to back down and
OL,7,Fended up opposing a barrister while
OL,8,Frepresenting himself at Leicester
OL,9,FCounty Court on July 11.
OL,11,FHe was awarded #200 compensation but
OL,12,Fhad to pay #180 court costs.
OL,14,FMr Richardson, from Rearsby,
OL,15,FLeicestershire, had parked his VW Golf
OL,16,Fin Town Square Car Park in Syston in
OL,17,F2020 but had no change on him and the
OL,18,Fcard payment machines were not working.
