OL,6,FHe then tried using the mobile phone
OL,7,Fapp - but received no notification to
OL,8,Fsay the payment had been successful,
OL,9,Fso feared it had not gone through.
OL,11,FHonest Mr Richardson wrote to the firm
OL,12,Fto explain what had happened and that
OL,13,Fhe might owe them #1 - but they
OL,14,Fresponded by immediately fining him
OL,15,F#100.
OL,17,FHe later found the receipt for his
OL,18,Fonline transaction in his junk email
OL,19,Ffolder and sent it to the firm as
OL,20,Fproof of payment.
