OL,6,FBut over the next four years debt
OL,7,Fcollection companies started sending
OL,8,Fhim letters threatening court action
OL,9,Fand the fine increased to #230.
OL,11,FSemi-retired Mr Richardson refused to
OL,12,Fback down and ended up opposing a
OL,13,Fbarrister while representing himself
OL,14,Fat Leicester County Court on July 11.
