OL,3,CMotorist wins five-year legal battle
OL,4,Cwith parking firm over a #1 ticket
OL,6,FMr Richardson said: "I got letters
OL,7,Ffrom various debt collectors. When I
OL,8,Fwrote to DCB Legal, who were pursuing
OL,9,Fthe debt, I told them I'd got the
OL,10,Freceipt now and they said it was up to
OL,11,FEuro Car Parks to drop it. I wrote to
OL,12,FEuro Car Parks and they told me it was
OL,13,Fup to DCB.
OL,15,F"DCB said they would see me in court,
OL,16,Fso I said, 'bring it on'."
OL,18,FITV News Central have contacted Euro
OL,19,FCar Parks for comment but are yet to
OL,20,Frespond.
